reviewText: Love it! Beautifully put together.  Very informative and eye opening. Its worth exploring your roots. You never know what you might find.

I really enjoyed watching this video.  It helped give me new ideas and paths to follow in researching my family's history which at best has been elusive.
The video was entertaining as well as informative.

I have been reseaching my family roots for over 14 years and I love this product because I can refer back to information
I need to review while doing reseach on the computer.
